      "turn_id": 1,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "我们需要为金融科技共识系统建一个类图，核心是要表达节点状态如何管理区块、投票和配置。我先从Checkpoint开始，它是整个共识的锚点，FinTech_LedgerService负责维护。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Checkpoint",
        "FinTech_LedgerService"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 2,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "Checkpoint作为锚点，那它和投票的关系是怎样的？是每个投票都要关联到一个Checkpoint吗？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Checkpoint",
        "VoteMessage"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 3,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "对，VoteMessage由FinTech_TransactionQueue产生，多个VoteMessage会归属到同一个Checkpoint，是多对一的关系。然后VoteMessage还需要被签名变成SignedVoteMessage，这个由FinTech_AuthVault处理。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "VoteMessage",
        "FinTech_TransactionQueue",
        "SignedVoteMessage",
        "FinTech_AuthVault"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 4,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "明白了，SignedVoteMessage和VoteMessage也是多对一。那区块Block怎么引入？它应该包含实际的区块体。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Block",
        "BlockBody"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 5,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "Block由FinTech_FraudDetection负责，它有个body字段指向BlockBody。关键是Block和SignedVoteMessage的关系——一个区块可以收集多个签名投票，同时一个签名投票也可能被多个区块引用，所以是多对多。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Block",
        "FinTech_FraudDetection",
        "SignedVoteMessage"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 6,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "好，我加上Block类，标注body: BlockBody，然后画Block和SignedVoteMessage之间的多对多关联。接下来是提案消息？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Block",
        "BlockBody",
        "SignedVoteMessage"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 7,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "对，ProposeMessage同样由FinTech_LedgerService处理。一个提案针对一个特定区块，但一个区块可能收到多个提案；同时提案也要携带一组签名投票来背书。",
      "elements_involved": [
